In this video, I'll bring you a home cooking recipe

鲫鱼汤
Carp Fish Soup

首先将鲫鱼清洗干净
First clean the fish

背部再打上花刀方便入味
Score the fish to make it easier to season

生姜排散之后 
Pat the ginger

挤出姜汁
and squeeze out the ginger juice

碗中加入适量的盐和料酒
Add a bit of salt and cooking wine into the bowl

将鲫鱼拌均之后腌制十分钟去腥
Mix well and marinate for 10 minutes to balance out the muddy taste in the fish.

下一步开始制作
Moving on

首先我们加入适量的油滑锅
First add a splash of oil and pour it out

然后加入少许的猪油
Then add a bit of pork lard

炒化
Melt it out


把腌制好的鲫鱼擦干水分
Dry the marinated fish

之后再放入锅中
Then put it into the pot

十秒钟之后再晃动鱼身
Shake it after ten seconds

开中火
Turn heat to medium

将鲫鱼的两面煎至金黄色
Till both sides are golden brown

然后加入开水没过鲫鱼
Then add boiling water over top of the fish

开大火将鲫鱼烧至浓白
Turn up the heat till soup is creamy white

然后转小火煮5分钟
Then turn heat to low and boil for 5 minutes

五分钟之后加入白玉菇
After 5 minutes add shimeji mushroom

白玉菇煮熟之后
After mushroom is cooked

加入盐和白胡椒粉调味
Season with salt and white pepper

调好味道之后即可出锅
Now we are ready to serve it.

一道非常鲜美营养的鲫鱼汤制作完成了
A delicious and nutritious Carp Fish Soup is done.


硬核家常菜
Hard Core Home Cooking
鲫鱼汤
Carp Fish Soup

鲫鱼
Carp

生姜、白玉菇
Ginger, Shimeji Mushroom

调料：盐、胡椒粉、料酒
Seasoning: Salt, Pepper, Cooking Wine

